rows.label: tlk43600143_04_msg0002
rows.name:
It's probably the tastiest thing I've
ever eaten in my life, and that's no
exaggeration!

rows.label: tlk43600143_04_msg0003
rows.name:
First time I tasted it, it almost moved
me to tears, it was so delicious.

rows.label: tlk43600143_04_msg0004
rows.name:
Never thought us working with
Superbia would introduce us
to a delicacy like that!

rows.label: tlk43600143_04_msg0005
rows.name:
The way I see it, Alst's going to pot
anyway, so I may as well blow all my
savings on the food.

rows.label: tlk43600143_04_msg0006
rows.name:
I ain't got that many years on the
clock left, but experiencing food like
that, I think I can go happy now.
